{"tid":636840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔係講笑】印部長「偉論」：我哋千幾年前已發明互聯網","createTime":"2018-04-21T09:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T14:36:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c221bb8d204841425315a21e8ff318b1a6104f9a","tid":636840,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/171831_5fd5fd484a9188f389b373fa9ba11e1e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F171831_5fd5fd484a9188f389b373fa9ba11e1e.png&h=c01293b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n震驚全人類🤯<br />\n【唔係講笑】印部長「偉論」：我哋千幾年前已發明互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2vxbtAb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vxbtAb&d=fchuQbFKY0nEdUBkMLtXEsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=bb63696a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2vxbtAb</a>"},{"pid":"e57449654ca622889d91b3806a521306e6e9247d","tid":636840,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"印度一名部長級官員日前發表「偉論」，聲稱互聯網是由千多年前的同胞發明，引來嘲笑揶揄，連學者也忍不住形容如此「反智」的言論出自官員之口，政府的管治令人擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n特里普拉邦（Tripura）首席部長德布（Biplab Deb）在一個公開場合「引經據典」指是古印度人發明互聯網。他以公元8世紀史詩《摩訶婆羅多》（Mahabharata）為例，指詩中角色桑加亞（Sanjaya）向國王逐一描述了發生在遙遠地方的戰事。儘管《摩訶婆羅多》以大量神話和寓言故事組成，但德布認為桑加亞可以清楚說出正在發生的事，足以「證明」古印度文明已存在互聯網及衞星科技技術。<br />\n<br />\n經濟學家魯帕（Rupa Subramanya）形容德布的言論令人擔憂，「部分執政印度人民黨（BJP）黨員接連發表反智和倒退言論，令人震驚和擔憂。與其解決今時今日的問題，他們忙於美化從未發生的虛構歷史，真是可憐及尷尬。」<br />\n<br />\n南亞歷史助理教授特魯希克（Audrey Truschke）在社交網諷刺德布：「當Siri已經可以這樣做的時候，為甚麼桑加亞還要說出戰爭經過？而且，當時人們應該早可以在facebook直播戰事了。」<br />\n<br />\n德布雖然引來嘲笑，但仍然堅持己見，更反指質疑他的人是容不下他人的意見，思想狹隘。"},{"pid":"fd5fef3456da92392ae3e33e4c879c3549beaa05","tid":636840,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c67622a939f4b9f638cfbf3c31ae4ae1194997e","tid":636840,"uid":173852,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:52:27.000Z","msg":"德布雖然引來嘲笑，但仍然堅持己見，更反指<span style=\"color: red;\">質疑他的人是容不下他人的意見，思想狹隘。</span><br />\n<br />\n好有即視感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781bcda40cf8289061803e5e0fc71b9b2c116214","tid":636840,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:53:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f151801cd4093f8c903ade3f43ba5d70ba49aaf","tid":636840,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c62a2eac6cfe036a820135093d84b2169934a5","tid":636840,"uid":143499,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"中國終於輸一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺打飛機方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bbcb7fdbfc9d0c27037fe584ca99931798b6b9","tid":636840,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0664042632267d406c43a1e4748d931f5a93d2","tid":636840,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"佢好明顯唔知咩係互聯網啦<br />\n分分鐘意為維基百科啲資料係水晶球占卜出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce3d0cf6b763e9ca92cfca5f9291d78441cd7bf","